org.vngx.jsch.proxy

Class ProxySOCKS4

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.vngx.jsch.proxy.AbstractProxy
      • org.vngx.jsch.proxy.ProxySOCKS4
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Proxy

    public class ProxySOCKS4
extends AbstractProxy
    Implementation of Proxy for proxying a connection using the SOCKS4 protocol. This file depends on following documents: SOCKS: A protocol for TCP proxy across firewalls, Ying-Da Lee http://www.socks.nec.com/protocol/socks4.protocol
    Author:
    Atsuhiko Yamanaka, Michael Laudati
